Package: inspectr
Type: Package
Title: Storing, manipulating and analysis spectroscopy and associated data in R.
Version: 0.3-14
Date: 2013-02-25
Author: Pierre Roudier <pierre.roudier@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Pierre Roudier <pierre.roudier@gmail.com>
Description: Stores and eases the manipulation of spectra and associated data, with dedicated classes for spatial and soil-related datasets.
URL: http://inspectr.r-forge.r-project.org/
Depends: R (>= 2.14)
Imports: methods, plyr, reshape2, stringr, sp, baseline, signal
Suggests: ggplot2, pls, RColorBrewer, chemometrics, aqp
License: GPL
LazyData: true
